+endpoints the v1+checkpoints round-trip group already exercises — and because the
+level is no longer claiming "mandatory v1," the earlier v1-vs-v1+roles worry about
+idea/variant seeding dissolves: `v1+durability` may freely read/seed any required
+v0 wire surface. The §13 MUST itself remains a universal deployment obligation
+(every conforming deployment MUST satisfy it); the level is just the suite's
+*verification* of its wire-observable projection for IUTs that expose the hook.
